  <item nodeId="node-1">
    <command xml:space="preserve">DetectiveAlfonzoAndTheCultOfLaMancha</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">You wake up from a quick nap in your office. You look around - you clearly haven't cleaned it in a while. How could you, with the biggest case you've ever faced still unsolved?&#x000A;&#x000A;Detective Afonzo and The Cult of La Mancha&#x000A;An Interactive Fiction by Alien Cat Studios&#x000A;Release 1 / Serial number 260525 / Inform 7 v10.1.2 / D&#x000A;&#x000A;Office&#x000A;My office, where I've solved so many crimes... but now I face my biggest mystery.&#x000A;&#x000A;You can see a desk, a closet (closed) and a rack (on which are a green hat, a red hat, a black hat, a tiara and a trophy) here.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-2"/>
      <child nodeId="node-7"/>
      <child nodeId="node-8"/>
      <child nodeId="node-31"/>
    </children>
  </item>
